[I] Reliable UDP networking library

[T] ENet's purpose is to provide a relatively thin, simple and robust network
[T] communication layer on top of UDP (User Datagram Protocol). The primary
[T] feature it provides is optional reliable, in-order delivery of packets.

[U] http://enet.bespin.org/

